{"tid":811581,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[義教 - DSE 數學科] 一連四堂免費終極補底班 ​","createTime":"2018-09-09T03:09:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:41:15.000Z","uid":178639,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"656276365414af3ef325b12857a74da98cd90dfe","tid":811581,"uid":178639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:09:07.000Z","msg":"而家好多補習社淨係睇錢，同一班乜學生都教、質素參差、教學無乜針對性。古語有云：教學最緊要係因材施教，如果教與學都無針對性，學生就好難有進步<br />\n<br />\n本人幫人私補六年，知道好多學生唔係科科都追求5**。特別係數學咁好多文科人其實淨係需要拎個3，但係讀起上黎好似力不從心。今次想開班義教，免費幫數學底唔好既大家，教大家點樣可以用最少既努力確保自己可以拎得Lv. 3/4，其餘時間就可以留返係自己主力科目。當然如果大家有興趣我都會教大家點樣循序漸進拎返個5**<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n中六同學仔，如果你預計自己DSE數學成績徘徊係lv. 1／2／ 3，呢個就非常啱你<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既，可以係下面留底tg. 或者 <a href=\"https://t.me/Kenneth_mat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKenneth_mat&d=Zdays%2Fva7Gj8FXNPFS381f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=34c57015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Kenneth_mat</a><br />\n<br />\n​"},{"pid":"1c2f6639896ba37c921ec7981d7904b35fa71481","tid":811581,"uid":205143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c450cc092590c12ea18a950fdf0f516b4826fa27","tid":811581,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T06:27:30.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"4a641d14c473a31a438e51a308b71667b0221d14","tid":811581,"uid":198822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T07:12:09.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"d46712ae349a6c865a461b593af201049ae4c330","tid":811581,"uid":178639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4e4baf036fb255783e5feff6705258ad90924cc","tid":811581,"uid":7001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:41:15.000Z","msg":"巴打改咗tg?"}]}